{"tid":1926363,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"宋智孝爆「希澈回訊講MOMO這句」全場笑翻","createTime":"2020-03-15T05:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T12:20:43.000Z","uid":74065,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"96c3881d00645da56cf074ca2755e208a7c562e7","tid":1926363,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4758/d4758500.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4758%2Fd4758500.jpg&h=feef102d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲宋智孝和金武烈登上《認識的哥哥》。（圖／翻攝自《認識的哥哥》官網）<br />\n<br />\n金武烈先談到是《認識的哥哥》真正的熱血觀眾，結果李壽根就突然站起來問「如果真的很喜歡，那現在（班上）有個深陷愛情的人，那個人是誰」，結果金武烈和宋智孝都秒回「金希澈」，話題瞬間帶到戀愛話題，讓希澈也忍不住露出驚慌的表情。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4758/d4758498.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4758%2Fd4758498.jpg&h=6e6bd6fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲李壽根故意提起公開戀愛中的希澈。（圖／翻攝自JTBC Entertainment YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n宋智孝被問到在希澈認愛時有沒有聯絡對方時，她笑說：「我有傳訊息給他，說恭喜你啊，希澈回說『謝謝妳，姐姐』，但後面一句讓我印象太深刻了，『MOMO是很不錯的人』。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4758/4758499.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4758%2F4758499.jpg&h=1d68dedd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲宋智孝說金希澈回她「MOMO是很不錯的人」。（圖／翻攝自JTBC Entertainment YouTube）<br />\n<br />\n希澈以緊張狀態聆聽突然聽到這句時整個人傻眼「我哪～（有）」，最後憑藉著流利口才將話題轉到別處，結果還是被姜虎東擺了一道，影片曝光後引起熱烈討論，相當逗趣。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1j0Tl-6SPQY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1j0Tl-6SPQY&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyWINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=c81c74fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1j0Tl-6SPQY</a><br />\nMOMO不錯哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871158d775a8b48c191995a7cdcf7634be9d764a","tid":1926363,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:35:53.000Z","msg":"傻閪希澈成日都要提起momo on99"},{"pid":"93bc3635fd9adbf23cc5f9ab6fd68f6cd68aaef6","tid":1926363,"uid":117802,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"871158d775a8b48c191995a7cdcf7634be9d764a","tid":1926363,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:35:53.000Z","msg":"傻閪希澈成日都要提起momo on99"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"你中文攞U?"},{"pid":"e348a10b232a0c622de45b34cf86f460f6eef655","tid":1926363,"uid":256952,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"871158d775a8b48c191995a7cdcf7634be9d764a","tid":1926363,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:35:53.000Z","msg":"傻閪希澈成日都要提起momo on99"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/37gjioH.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F37gjioH.gif&h=2b304c24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea3b9521576854b8488b61cde7a92fe0c8c71c07","tid":1926363,"uid":46435,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:43:27.000Z","msg":"希澈老師都係個不錯的人.."},{"pid":"b58a20eacf2e19c2c0674214c5930e18f6ee686e","tid":1926363,"uid":256952,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"93bc3635fd9adbf23cc5f9ab6fd68f6cd68aaef6","tid":1926363,"uid":117802,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"871158d775a8b48c191995a7cdcf7634be9d764a","tid":1926363,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:35:53.000Z","msg":"傻閪希澈成日都要提起momo on99"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:37:24.000Z","msg":"你中文攞U?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T05:44:46.000Z","msg":"呢啲劇本梗係私底下溝通左先架喇 少年你太年輕了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"